<p>Glad to introduce a new feature, <em><strong>CodeBox</strong></em>, on Green Shoes.<p />CodeBox is almost the same as EditBox, but has two more functions:<p />- line number<br />- syntax highlighting<p />CodeBox was <a href="https://github.com/mohawkjohn/green_shoes/commit/01f1b9782b00d51aa58f95b5de5d2002f2c24fa7">originally</a> written by <a href="https://github.com/mohawkjohn">John</a>. Thanks!<p /> Let's enjoy happy coding with Green Shoes! :-D<p />ashbb</p>]]></content:encoded>
